status: MARC21-007: Completeness of the motion picture
Whether or not the item being cataloged is judged to be complete.

definition (en): Completeness is not applicable to the type of motion picture.
scope note (en): E.g., home movies, unedited footage, outtakes, and in some cases, unidentified material, etc.

definition (en): Completeness of the item is not known.
